<!--

========================
Features:
========================
 - Widget to perform a search
 - Placing the widget in a group will limit the object search to the group and the users search to members of this group 

========================
Notes:
========================
- Only Tags custom search is enabled (so no comments)
- Searching from within a group for users based on tags will not work (only regular user search)
- If, for example, a search only should result in blogs, also blogs with a tag matching the search query is listed, but the more "+6 more tag" link will not result in a list of blogs with tags, but all object with tags 

